            </div>

            <div
              class="retro-panel rounded-xl border border-[#3a4568] bg-[#0c1024] p-4"
            >
              <p
                class="font-arcade text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.25em] text-[#bfe9ff] sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.28em]"
              >
                ERROR TRACE
              </p>
              <pre
                class="font-arcade mt-3 text-[0.6rem] leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-wrap text-[#f7f4ff] sm:text-xs">
MODULE: UPLINK.DRV
STATUS: LOCKOUT_PROTOCOL
STAMP: 2026-02-02 23:59:59
PACKETS LOST: 04
CRC MISMATCH: TRUE
